{"tid":1463692,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］姐夫由旺角坐地鐵到佐敦，身體出現不適","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:35:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:29:22.000Z","uid":260328,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"38f451ac441a66fffca91b00ac96161d4f5cc274","tid":1463692,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姐夫岩岩坐左MTR 旺角去佐敦，途中佢有渣扶手，電梯都係，家姐岩岩上兩個月生左小朋友，姐夫要幫手睇B,次次遊行都係安全既情況走，未食過彈。<br />\n岩岩佢坐完地鐵有咁既情況發生，好似俾蚊咬咁，腫同痕，係咪啲催淚彈通過冷氣成條紅色線都有事？<br />\n<br />\n十分擔心，唔敢俾佢摸小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係咁 ？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VYr8sD1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVYr8sD1.jpg&h=89d7832b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0jNJcp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0jNJcp.jpg&h=3ff63233&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hhQ1ND6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhhQ1ND6.jpg&h=b05f91a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"053463ff46a36291a062f384ff6ec867b95893b2","tid":1463692,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"蟲咬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbbf7f650de1d5b7d2da35c17bab8c9be6874a5","tid":1463692,"uid":260328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"053463ff46a36291a062f384ff6ec867b95893b2","tid":1463692,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:18:07.000Z","msg":"蟲咬?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:19:06.000Z","msg":"蟲又唔會係咁咬一個位<img src=\"/assets/face